"title": "5638: writing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5638",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A form of communication, including the writing of books, letters and scrolls. Many kinds of materials have been written on. Figuratively speaking, the heart can be written on.</p>\n<h2>Uses of writing</h2>\n<h3>Books</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:2\">JER 30:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:3\">LUK 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>The law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:24\">DEU 31:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:26\">JOS 24:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:21\">2KI 23:21</a></p>\n<h3>Annals and records</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:41\">1KI 11:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:19\">2KI 12:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:29\">1CH 29:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:25\">2CH 35:25</a></p>\n<h3>Agreements</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:38\">NEH 9:38</a></p>\n<h3>Legal documents</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:1\">DEU 24:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:4\">MRK 10:4</a></p>\n<h3>Letters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:14\">2SA 11:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:22\">ROM 16:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:18\">COL 4:18</a></strong> <em>In those days the sender would add a few words to a letter dictated to and written by a secretary.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:8-1Kgs21:11\">1KI 21:8–21:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:12\">EST 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:11\">GAL 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:1\">2PE 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>Writing materials</h2>\n<h3>Stone</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:15-Exod32:16\">EXO 32:15–32:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:2-Deut27:3\">DEU 27:2–27:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:24\">JOB 19:24</a></p>\n<h3>Wood</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num17:2-Num17:3\">NUM 17:2–17:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:9\">DEU 6:9</a></p>\n<h3>Metal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:20\">ZEC 14:20</a></p>\n<h3>Walls</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5-Dan5:8\">DAN 5:5–5:8</a></p>\n<h3>Writing tablets</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:2\">HAB 2:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:63\">LUK 1:63</a></p>\n<h3>Scrolls</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:18\">DEU 17:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:11\">REV 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:14\">EXO 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:23\">NUM 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:23\">JOB 19:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:1\">ISA 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:18\">JER 36:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:60\">JER 51:60</a></p>\n<h2>Writing kits</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:2-Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:2–9:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:11\">EZK 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:12\">2JN 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:13\">3JN 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>God writes</h2>\n<h3>The law</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:18\">EXO 31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:15-Exod32:16\">EXO 32:15–32:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:1\">EXO 34:1</a></p>\n<h3>Figurative writing of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:16\">PSA 139:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps87:6\">PSA 87:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:20\">LUK 10:20</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ writes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:6\">JHN 8:6</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Writing on the heart</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33\">JER 31:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:10\">HEB 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:16\">HEB 10:16</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:15\">ROM 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:3\">PRO 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:3\">PRO 7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:1\">JER 17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:2\">2CO 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>General references to writing</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:1\">GEN 5:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:19\">DEU 31:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh18:4\">JOS 18:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:4\">2CH 35:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:18\">PSA 102:18</a></p>",
